# Last update (home screen)

Whenever you change app behaviour or UI in a way that is worth tracking on the **main screen** (`App.tsx`), update **`src/app/lastUpdate.ts`**:

- Set `LAST_UPDATE_DISPLAY` to the current date/time (e.g. run `date '+%d %b %Y, %H:%M'` and paste the result).
- Commit that file together with the rest of the change so GitHub Pages and reviewers see a fresh stamp.

Do not leave `lastUpdate.ts` stale across meaningful commits.
